sqlReaderQuery.value:
with lead as
(select distinct SaleforceLeadID,IsDeleted from
 [Reports].[Funnel]
where [OriginalCampaignAgency] in (@{pipeline().parameters.AgencyName}) and ( LeadCreateDateEST >= DATEADD(day, -90, GETDATE()) or ActivityDateEST >= DATEADD(day, -90, GETDATE())
or dateadd(mi,datepart(tz,CONVERT(datetime,[ReportCreateDate])    AT TIME ZONE 'Eastern Standard Time'),[ReportCreateDate]) >= DATEADD(day, -90, GETDATE()) and IsDeleted = 0)
)
select a.[FunnelTransactionID]
      ,a.[SalesForceTaskID]
      ,a.[BrightPatternID]
      ,a.[LeadFunnelTransactionID]
      ,a.[SaleforceLeadID]  as [SalesForceLeadID]
      ,a.[Company]
      ,a.[FunnelStep]
      ,a.[Funnelstatus]
      ,a.[OriginalGCLID]
      ,a.[LeadCreateDateEST]
      ,a.[ActivityDateEST]
      ,a.[Date]
      ,a.[Time]
      ,a.[DayPart]
      ,a.[Hour]
      ,a.[Minute]
      ,a.[Seconds]
      ,a.[OriginalContactType]
      ,a.[OriginalSourcecode]
      ,a.[OriginalDialedNumber]
      ,a.[OriginalPhoneNumberAreaCode]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignAgency]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignChannel]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignName]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignFormat]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignLanguage]
      ,a.[OriginalCampaignPromotionCode]

      ,a.[OriginalCampaignEndDate]

      ,a.[RecentSourcecode]

      ,a.[RecentCampaignName]

      ,a.[RecentCampaignLanguage]
      ,a.[RecentCampaignPromotionCode]

      ,a.[RecentCampaignEndDate]
      ,a.[RecentCampaignStatus]
      ,a.[PostalCode]
      ,a.[Region]
      ,a.[MarketDMA]
      ,a.[CenterName]
      ,a.[CenterRegion]
      ,a.[CenterDMA]
      ,a.[CenterType]
      ,a.[CenterOwner]
      ,a.[Language]
      ,a.[Gender]
      ,a.[Ethnicity]
      ,a.[HairLossCondition]
      ,a.[MaritalStatus]
      ,a.[Occupation]
      ,a.[BirthYear]
      ,a.[AgeBands]
      ,a.[NewContact]
      ,a.[NewLead]
      ,a.[NewAppointment]
      ,a.[NewShow]
      ,a.[NewSale]
      ,a.[NewLeadToAppointment]
      ,a.[NewLeadToShow]
      ,a.[NewLeadToSale]
      ,a.[QuotedPrice]
      ,a.[PrimarySolution]
      ,a.[DoNotContactFlag]
      ,a.[DoNotCallFlag]
      ,a.[DoNotSMSFlag]
      ,a.[DoNotEmailFlag]
      ,a.[DoNotMailFlag]
      ,a.[IsDeleted]
from [Reports].[Funnel] a
      inner join lead b on a.SaleforceLeadID=b.SaleforceLeadID
where funnelstep='Lead' and b.IsDeleted = 0
union all
select a.[FunnelTransactionID]
      ,a.[SalesForceTaskID]
      ,a.[BrightPatternID]
      ,a.[LeadFunnelTransactionID]
      ,a.[SaleforceLeadID] as [SalesForceLeadID]
      ,a.[Company]

      ,a.[LeadCreateDateEST]

      ,a.[Date]

      ,a.[DoNotMailFlag]

from [Reports].[Funnel] a
where funnelstep!='Lead' and SaleforceLeadID in (select SaleforceLeadID from lead ) and IsDeleted = 0
